Description:
    Integrates and configures the html editor "redactor" for the Infopark inplace editing. The
    editor comes with its own icon font for its editing buttons.

Example:
    `rails generate cms:component:editing:redactor`

    Assets:
      app/assets/fonts/redactor_icons.eot
      app/assets/fonts/redactor_icons.ttf
      app/assets/fonts/redactor_icons.woff

      app/assets/javascripts/redactor.config.js
      app/assets/javascripts/redactor.js

      app/assets/stylesheets/redactor.css.less

    Misc: Extends the application.js manifest.
